Sensational Iconic Corset Mister Pearl for Thierry Mugler Semi Sheer Bodice

About the Item

Holy Grail. Iconic Muesum Worthy Collectors Piece Extremely rare spectacular Corset created by the One And Only Mister Pearl for Thierry Mugler. Kylie Minogue absolutely killing it in this fabulous wearable Art. A true example of the grande Art of Corsetterie. Gorgeous semi sheer powder/nude Corset top with lacing on the back. Could be worn both ways. Stunning Construction to shape and hug the body. Adjustable size due to lacing, best for small size XS/S maybe M please see measurement on picture This truly is wearable Art. Extremely rare collectors piece. Highly wearable and an investment piece that will continue to increase in value.
